	<h1 class="title">为何又升级？微信每次深得你心，就赢了世界</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马宁忆</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-15 15:59:55 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1886/medium/1886.jpg?1436646427" alt="" />			
	</div>
